Priscilla Moran https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Priscilla_Moran 0 Priscilla Moran (November 23, 1917 – November 11, 2006) was an American silent film actress. She was born in Sedalia, Missouri. She made her film debut in 1922, and retired from the silver screen in 1937 at the age of 20, having appeared in fourteen films.
